Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來是今天關東地區的天氣預報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由於受到西部而來的低氣壓影響
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到了夜晚局部地區可能會有降雨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}差不多就這些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}建議出門時帶上雨傘…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼要離開櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繼續待在櫻花莊裡的話 我就會變得討厭自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}討厭？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我要離開櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從一開始我就是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新人獎的截稿日期快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會為你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到離開櫻花莊為止 我都會繼續照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名一如既往的通宵進行作畫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畫了又改 畫了又改的重複著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像直到新人獎截稿日期的當天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才終於完成了原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\fs20\fn華康竹風體W4\shad0\c&H847D77&\frz10.16\pos(676.715,179.571)}吃完之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\fs20\fn華康竹風體W4\shad0\c&H847D77&\frz12.33\pos(700.716,233.287)}稍微睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關於幫貓尋找飼主的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在也只剩下小光和小望了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然很遺憾 但相信今晚無法看到銀河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就這樣 朝著搬到普通宿舍的這個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總算又往前邁進了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這身打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅此而已嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟什麼的最討厭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:01:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是青澀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「好可愛啊」「受不了啦」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「讓人好想玩惡代官遊戲」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們是想聽你說說這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}參雜了性騷擾發言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說這是要過七夕用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H2C566C&\frz18\move(410,577,411,-8,28,3865)}學弟專用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H304652&\frz18.5\move(842,625,842,90,25,3445)}向夜空許願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H304652&\frz18.5\move(723,760,723,340,27,2905)}你的夢想是什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美咲要我轉交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛤？
Comment: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}一回目　まぐれで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:49.89,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}第一次邂逅 若是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}二回目ってどうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:53.20,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那麼第二次 又是如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}偶然じゃないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.90,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}果然並非偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}三回 目が合うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.63,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}第三次 彼此注視之時
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.05,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}真是個怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.15,0:03:07.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}割とみんな言うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:07.55,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}大家意外的異口同聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}気になったことは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}但這就是我在意他的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:14.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}違うんだ そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:14.76,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不對啦 才不是那裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:18.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}君は多分　純粋で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:18.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}你恐怕十分的純粹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:21.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}純粋を曲げず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.44,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}不願扭曲自身的純粹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:28.64,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}だから小さな日常にさえ立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:28.64,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}所以就連瑣碎的日常 你也依然毫不退步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:32.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:32.55,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}那些帶來夢想的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:35.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}足りない夢の在り処
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}描繪夢想缺失的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:39.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}一定就像是這樣開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:42.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.80,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}嶄新而又精彩的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:46.25,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}夢を持ってきた言葉を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:46.31,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}就把那些帶來夢想的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}知らない振りしてゆこう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.91,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}拋於身後裝作不聞不知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}トキメキと夢の在り処
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:54.30,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur4}出發前往精彩夢境的所在
