Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然還是想留在油菜花莊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是椎名所期望的 真正的Happy End
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼在這種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太 接一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您好 這是椎名的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 您好 剛才受您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名 椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒醒 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她說出道的事定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}傻瓜 當然是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說沒能拿到新人獎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:20:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但只要修改一下原稿的話 下個月就能刊登了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來已經改好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明應該很高興 眼淚卻流了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得好好慶祝一下出道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 我有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 那個我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我從沒直呼過女生的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美咲的名字你明明是直接叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}千尋也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是亞馬遜女野人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不公平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青澀 太青澀了 空太！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是青春啊 令人心跳不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大姊姊我可是為你們捏了一把汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等 等等…你們是從什麼時候開始聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 我有話想要對你說！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur5}心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從最開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼什麼 快說啊快說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你也有話要對我們說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啦好啦 不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一口氣把自己真實的想法喊出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給…給你們添麻煩了 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請讓我再一次…留在櫻花莊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白 恭喜你成功出道！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And 歡迎學弟回家！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把毫無起伏的日子 歸咎於他人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.31,0:22:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:25.28,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}過ぎるだけの  時間じゃ悔しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:25.28,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}一味流逝的時光 徒增懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要自己有心 世界會在一瞬之間改變顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.07,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}刻まなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.07,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}唯有銘記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}櫻花莊裡混雜著各式各樣的顏色 亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.33,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}「此処にいる」と心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:34.33,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}「我就在這裡」 內心如此吶喊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:37.83,Note,,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\shad0\fs43\frz288.1\c&H1F3042&\frx352\fry354\pos(917,179)\org(939,192)}希\N望\N空\N太\N的\N願\N望\N能\N夠\N實\N現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.83,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.83,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}I'm dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今後 這一點也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.46,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}迷いながら  涙を飲み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:43.46,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an9}不斷迷茫著 逞強噙住眼角淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:49.59,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an2}不器用だね　夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.96,0:22:49.59,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3\an2}真是笨拙呢 連夢想都不斷繞道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.96,0:22:49.84,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1300,0)\bord2.4\fs42\3c&HE6E6E6&\c&HB97BE2&\alpha&H00&\pos(1025,162)}色彩斑斕的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.60,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}大空を見上げ　何も見えず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:55.60,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}仰望這片廣闊的天空 卻無法確認一物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:03.90,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}胸が痛むわけ考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:03.90,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}也曾思考過內心會如此疼痛的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:05.48,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}DAYS  of  DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:05.48,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:08.28,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.48,0:23:08.28,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}飛奔而出 風聲過耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:14.70,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君と僕の中で　何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:14.70,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}在你與我的內心中 究竟有什麼開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:16.79,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}わからないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:16.79,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}雖然沒有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:24.38,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}キラキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:24.38,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是就朝著炫目陽光照耀的地方一直前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:30.26,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:30.26,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}雖然無法知道 何謂永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}『我是母的』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:41.02,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs43\b1\alpha&H00&\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\blur5\3c&HE0DC97&\pos(700,450))}櫻花莊的認真女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.35,0:23:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}『有種雌性會增加的預感』
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}…小光這樣說道
